# Project Structure Guide

This is a monorepo project managed with pnpm workspaces and Turborepo. The project consists of several key packages and directories:

## Core Packages
- [packages/cli](mdc:packages/cli) - Command-line interface package
- [packages/client](mdc:packages/client) - Client library package
- [packages/create-catalyst](mdc:packages/create-catalyst) - Project scaffolding tool
- [packages/eslint-config-catalyst](mdc:packages/eslint-config-catalyst) - Shared ESLint configuration

## Configuration Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package configuration
- [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml) - Workspace configuration
- [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json) - Turborepo configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration

